Version: 0.9.5
Revision: 1
Maintainer: David Fang <fangism@users.sourceforge.net>
Source: mirror:gnu:libunistring/libunistring-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: 1a705bcdcb83799d544137617b377cfd
